---
title: Feta-Beyond Meat® Meatballs  with Sundried Tomato Orzo
description: Dill-icious feta and spinach Beyond Meat® meatballs are the jewels in this Mediterranean dinner! Nestled on a bed of creamy sun-dried tomato pesto orzo, with a sprinkle of feta.
